description:
Jazz Journalists Association Awards 2012, 2011 & 2010 
Trumpeter of the Year Nominee Tom Harrell talks about why standards are important in jazz, bringing popularity to jazz and creating bonds with an audience.
fulltitle: Tom Harrell Creating Bonds with the Audience
title: Tom Harrell Creating Bonds with the Audience
